{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab G2G (Government to Government)\sa180\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 \outlinelevel2 \b \fs28 Scope\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab {\b In Scope:} Review and approval of government ICT projects; Enforcement of Government Enterprise Architecture (GEA); Implementation of national digital infrastructure; ICT standards development and compliance; Coordination of ICT programs across MDAs.\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab {\b Out of Scope:} Sector-specific service delivery systems operated by MDAs.\sa180\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 \outlinelevel2 \b \fs28 Triggers\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab A ministry, department, or agency proposes a new ICT system or digital platform.\sa180\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 \outlinelevel2 \b \fs28 End States\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab {\b Successful:} ICT system approved and deployed; System complies with national ICT standards; Government digital infrastructure expanded.\sa180\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 \outlinelevel2 \b \fs28 Policy Context\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab ICT Authority Act (2013); Kenya Digital Economy Blueprint; Government Enterprise Architecture (GEA) Framework; Data Protection Act (2019); National Cybersecurity Strategy.\sa180\par}
